project_descr: The Programme aims to contribute to an environment of trust and cooperation across the Nistru River, generating new perspectives on a shared future by people on both banks while responding to their pressing development needs.

outputs.output_descr: Foster increased cross-river cooperation of economic actors leading to improved employment opportunities and livelihoods across the Nistru River
Empower local communities and actors from both sides to participate in collaborative projects addressing pressing development needs and improving critical community infrastructure
Promoting Confidence in the Health Sector
